<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>EMA624_03_IH_0004</title>

		<!-- 공통 js-->
		<script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
		<script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

		<!-- 공통 css-->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

		<!-- 개별 -->
		<script src="./../../common_practice/js/ema624_02_ih_0005.js"></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema624_03.css" />
	</head>

	<body>
		<div id="app_wrap" class="ema624_03_ih_0004">
			<section class="title type2">
				<h2 data-head="4_deep_green" lang="y">간단한 자연수의 비로 옳게 나타낸 것을 찾아 기호를 써 보세요.</h2>
			</section>

			<section class="contents">
				<div class="question_box justify_center">
					<div class="img_area">
						<img src="./../../common_practice/img/EMA624_03_IH/0004_bg.png" alt="" />
						<ul class="text_area">
							<li>
								<i class="num_sign">ㄱ</i>
								0.8:2.7
								<img
									class="arrow"
									src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg"
									alt=""
								/>
								80:27
							</li>
							<li>
								<i class="num_sign">ㄴ</i>
								<div class="flex align_center">
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>5</span>
										<span>12</span>
									</div>
									<span>:</span>
									<div class="mixed_fraction">
										<span>1</span>
										<div class="fraction_box">
											<span>1</span>
											<span>6</span>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<img
									class="arrow"
									src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg"
									alt=""
								/>
								5:7
							</li>
							<li>
								<i class="num_sign">ㄷ</i>
								<div class="flex align_center">
									<span>3:</span>
									<div class="fraction_box">
										<span>2</span>
										<span>5</span>
									</div>
								</div>
								<img
									class="arrow"
									src="./../../common_practice/common/img/icon_arrow_right_navy.svg"
									alt=""
								/>
								15:2
							</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="boolean_wrap type_chk">
							<div>
								<button data-answer-single="false" class="button1"></button>
								<button data-answer-single="false" class="button2"></button>
								<button data-answer-single="true" class="button3"></button>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- 해설 -->
				<div class="solve_area">
					<div class="inner_solve">
						<div class="flex">
							<strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
							<div class="conts_solve">
								<div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
									<div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
										㉠ 0.8 : 2.7의 전항과 후항에 10을 곱하면 8 : 27이 됩니다.
									</div>
									<div class="fraction_txt mt_15" lang="y">
										㉡ 후항
										<div class="mixed_fraction">
											<span>1</span>
											<span class="fraction_box">
											<span>1</span>
											<span>6</span>
											</span>
										</div>을
										<span class="fraction_box">
										<span>7</span>
										<span>6</span>
										</span>로 바꾼 후
										<div class="operation_box">
											<span class="fraction_box">
												<span>5</span>
												<span>12</span>
											</span>
											<span>:</span>
											<span class="fraction_box">
												<span>7</span>
												<span>6</span>
											</span>
										</div>
										<span>의 전항과 후항에 12를 곱하면 5 : 14가 됩니다.</span>
									</div>
									<div class="fraction_txt mt_15" lang="y">
										㉢
										<div class="operation_box">
											<span>3:</span>
											<span class="fraction_box ml_0">
												<span>2</span>
												<span>5</span>
											</span>
										</div>
										의 전항과 후항에 5를 곱하면 15 : 2가 됩니다.
									</div>
									<div class="fraction_txt mt_15" lang="y">
										따라서 간단한 자연수의 비로 옳게 나타낸 것은 ㉢입니다.
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="buttons_solve"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="btn_area">
					<button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
					<button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
